message.body: Went to another game today?
Hahaha. Nah... Just watched a couple from home. Eagles didn't play today.
Had a relaxing Sunday then?
Today has been a long day....
It feels long! Are you okay? Must be rough to be back after a long weekend.
I'm leaving now so I'll be better in a bit. It really has been tough with the long break... How are you doing?
Just feeling foggy right now. I'm thinking it would have been nice to take go out for some fresh air today but it's getting dark.
It's raining out too, so watch out for that too. Gloomy end to the day.
Hahah does not help Monday'a reputation...
